&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Afresh, the AI platform for grocery, began by tackling the most complex problem in the industry: fresh, and has evolved into the core AI platform for grocers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By leveraging proprietary AI designed for high-volatility environments, we empower partners like Albertsons, Meijer, and Wakefern to drive smarter decisions across their entire enterprise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Following record-breaking 70% revenue growth in 2025, we have scaled to 6 enterprise-grade solutions, with solutions live in over 10% of the U.S. grocery market. Our platform now orchestrates billions of decisions from the store floor to the distribution center and prevented over 200 million pounds of food waste last year alone.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re looking for a role where your work directly translates into massive scale and social good, and you want to be part of the team that defines how the world eats, there is no better time to join us.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re seeking an&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Demand Generation Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to define and drive how Afresh shows up in the grocery market. This is a high-ownership role at the center of our go-to-market: you&#39;ll set the channel strategy, build end-to-end programs, and partner closely with sales to turn engagement into pipeline. We&#39;re looking for someone to help build a modern, AI-powered demand engine — with the autonomy to make real calls about where to invest, what to kill, how to reach customers at every stage of the sales cycle, and how to win.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What makes this work distinctive is our market. We sell to a defined set of enterprise grocery retailers, which means demand generation here is a craft of precision rather than volume. The best programs are sharp, well-targeted, and grounded in a clear point of view about our buyers. You&#39;ll have the space to design integrated campaigns that flex across top, middle, and bottom of funnel as the business evolves — and the mandate to bring a strong point of view on the AI tools and tactics shaping modern demand gen, and to evolve our stack with us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the Head of Marketing, you&#39;ll partner closely with Revenue Leadership and Sales, and manage an event coordinator responsible for pre-event logistics. You&#39;ll also work in tight partnership with our PMM team — they shape our positioning and content; you own how it reaches the right buyers, in the right format, at the right moment.&lt;/p&gt;
