&lt;li&gt;BS in Computer Science or equivalent experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6+ years of software development experience with &lt;strong&gt;4+ years dedicated to building complex, scalable frontends using React&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
